	<item>
		<title>5 Strategies for Scaling Your Business in 2026</title>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>Scaling a business requires deliberate strategy, not just hard work. In this post, we break down five proven strategies that have helped our clients achieve sustainable growth.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

		<!-- wp:heading {"level":3,"style":{"color":{"text":"#c9a96e"}}} -->
		<h3 class="wp-block-heading" style="color:#c9a96e">1. Invest in Your Core</h3>
		<!-- /wp:heading -->

		<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>Identify what makes your business unique and double down. The most successful companies we work with focus their resources on their core differentiator.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

		<!-- wp:heading {"level":3,"style":{"color":{"text":"#c9a96e"}}} -->
		<h3 class="wp-block-heading" style="color:#c9a96e">2. Build Systems, Not Dependencies</h3>
		<!-- /wp:heading -->

		<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>Document your processes and build scalable systems. This ensures consistency as you grow and reduces your reliance on any single team member.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[Proven strategies that have helped our clients achieve sustainable double-digit growth through deliberate focus and systematic execution.]]></excerpt:encoded>
		<wp:post_type>post</wp:post_type>
		<wp:post_name>scaling-strategies-2026</wp:post_name>
		<wp:status>publish</wp:status>
