	</item>

	<item>
		<title>How We Helped a Client Achieve 300% Growth</title>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>When a mid-market retail client came to us with stagnant revenue, we knew the solution required a complete operational overhaul. Over 18 months, we restructured their supply chain, revamped their digital presence, and rebuilt their sales team.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

		<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>The result? A 300% increase in revenue, 45% reduction in operational costs, and a team that's now equipped to sustain that growth independently.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[How a complete operational overhaul led to a 300% revenue increase and 45% cost reduction for a mid-market retail client.]]></excerpt:encoded>
